The map points towards the end of the world ♫

12
00:01:06,880 --> 00:01:12,620
♫ Some day, we'll finally arrive ♫

13
00:01:12,620 --> 00:01:17,130
♫ Distant roads ♫

14
00:01:17,130 --> 00:01:21,580
♫ So moving ♫

